<i>verb</i>: 확인하다 [화긴하다], 확언하다 [화건하다], 긍정하다 [긍정하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>확인하다 [화긴하다]</dt><br>
<dd>check; affirm; confirm; verify</dd><br>
<dd>틀림없이 그러한지를 알아보거나 인정하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To find out if something is true or admit that it is true.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>확언하다 [화건하다]</dt><br>
<dd>assert; guarantee; affirm</dd><br>
<dd>틀림없이 그러하다고 말하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To say that something is definitely true.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>긍정하다 [긍정하다]</dt><br>
<dd>affirm; acknowledge</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사실이나 생각을 맞다거나 옳다고 인정하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To accept that a fact or thought is right or true.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>